      <title>Hard Road Ahead for Brazil</title>

      <description>Brazilians who celebrated President Dilma Rousseff’s ouster from office Thursday now confront a sobering economic and political picture, with a narrow window for change under a new but no less unpopular leader, Michel Temer.</description>
